data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET !!! REDUCED TO APPRAISED VALUE (Certified appraisal given upon request) MOVE IN READY Just painted inside !!  Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious Gated golf course community of Hunters Green, a highly sought-after Master Planned Community in the heart of New Tampa. This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage residence offers over 1,980 square feet of  living space, making it the perfect place to call home. As you approach, you'll immediately notice the beautiful landscaping and charm of this property. Situated on a peaceful conservation lot, this home boasts a serene and picturesque setting. The PVC fenced yard provides both privacy and security, making it an ideal space for children and pets to play. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the elegance of high ceilings and an abundance of natural light that fills the living room and family room. Whether you're hosting a gathering or enjoying a quiet evening, this home provides the perfect backdrop for any occasion. The beautiful breakfast nook is a delightful place to start your day, bathed in the warm glow of morning light. The well-appointed kitchen offers black appliances. Washer and dryer are staying with the house. For added peace of mind, this home comes equipped with a hardwired 5500W Generator, ensuring you'll never be without power during unexpected outages. Hunters Green is known for its exclusive amenities, and this home is no exception. The community offers a 24-hour manned gated entrance, a neighborhood park, and a private Country Club with a golf course. There are also playgrounds, picnic areas, tennis courts, baseball and soccer fields, and so much more, providing endless opportunities for recreation and relaxation. Beyond the community's gates, you'll find this New Tampa location to be incredibly convenient. Easy access to I-75 makes commuting a breeze, and you'll be in close proximity to top-rated schools, a variety of restaurants, and shopping destinations, including the Shops at Wiregrass. Medical facilities, including Moffitt Cancer Center and the VA hospital, are just a short drive away, ensuring you have access to top-notch healthcare. For outdoor enthusiasts, the nearby Flatwoods Park offers scenic trails for hiking and biking. Whether you're seeking the tranquility of a conservation lot or the excitement of a vibrant community, this home offers it all. Don't miss your opportunity to experience the best of New Tampa living in this exquisite Hunters Green residence. Schedule your viewing today and make this house your forever home.
